content: It great for my Lil bro!
Update: We've been contacted by Thup and they will refund the price of the game. Does not work on Samsung S7 Edge. It was completely unplayable for my son. The graphics blink in and out. :-(
Got a nexus 5 and the game just flashes on and off on the screen. Unplayable.

Usually I absolutely love Thup's Monkey preschool games, but this particular one was just no good in my opinion. The movement of the objects on the screen were rather jerky, which kinda gave me a headache after just a minute of play. To be honest, I feel like usually Thup puts quite a bit of effort into the quality of the art used for their games, but this one felt very subpar on pretty much all of the artwork. I felt like it was the quality you would see for a $0.99 game or possibly even a free game.
